    "rowsha": "tLLoLvvRKdviGSzKCa67+f2/u0Tnmi0iH4UDhyihrXc=",
    "originContent": "## How to contribute",
    "translatedContent": "## কেনেকৈ সহায় কৰিব"
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "3eiI4JSh6a5iRQ68O9mDmDdXyUqyMKwHpUo/FFjC8m0=",
    "originContent": "Setup your machine for developing tauri v1 applications: [Tauri prerequisites](https://tauri.app/v1/guides/getting-started/prerequisites)",
    "translatedContent": "আপোনাৰ মেচিনত tauri v1 এপ্লিকেশ্যন ডেভেলপ কৰাৰ বাবে ছেটআপ কৰক: [Tauri prerequisites](https://tauri.app/v1/guides/getting-started/prerequisites)"
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "qa8hwKJAfVCCr1Ubl0hebJSvMxxeZmgguzhgWZPNtYM=",
    "originContent": "</br></br>",
    "translatedContent": "</br></br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "o9ZpogYO9CbX6qBgSQ/nkvognmsHDOPW/TjfW8uYloU=",
    "originContent": "When this is done just do ```git clone https://github.com/RickyDane/CoDriver``` or ```gh repo clone RickyDane/CoDriver``` in a location on your machine.",
    "translatedContent": "এইটো হোৱা পিছত কেৱল ```git clone https://github.com/RickyDane/CoDriver``` বা ```gh repo clone RickyDane/CoDriver``` আপোনাৰ মেচিনৰ যিকোনো ঠাইত কৰক।"
  },
  {
    "row": 78,
    "rowsha": "qa8hwKJAfVCCr1Ubl0hebJSvMxxeZmgguzhgWZPNtYM=",
    "originContent": "</br></br>",
    "translatedContent": "</br></br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 79,
    "rowsha": "qsgMb8yXuMkDrC/0L/NH6qJcfcdht0AY0bfcm4QWkVY=",
    "originContent": "You should be able to run ```cargo tauri dev``` in the root directory of this project to start building and running CoDriver.",
    "translatedContent": "আপুনি এই প্ৰজেক্টৰ মূল ডিৰেক্টৰীত ```cargo tauri dev``` চলাই CoDriver নিৰ্মাণ আৰু চলাব পাৰিব।"
  },
  {
    "row": 80,
    "rowsha": "7s9q1NJ/yyokhTktGw5lSs/FO1fQ83HZfNVIsHV8n9c=",
    "originContent": "</br>",
    "translatedContent": "</br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 81,
    "rowsha": "QZn89KM2rdFDkEEm/SZkHHJAqUpNfKIAHc8qqwByndg=",
    "originContent": "Be sure to have tauri-cli installed: ```cargo install tauri-cli```",
    "translatedContent": "নিশ্চিত কৰক যে tauri-cli ইনষ্টল কৰা আছে: ```cargo install tauri-cli```"
  },
  {
    "row": 82,
    "rowsha": "7s9q1NJ/yyokhTktGw5lSs/FO1fQ83HZfNVIsHV8n9c=",
    "originContent": "</br>",
